    IPRFRQ 10 ISVFRQ 10 IHTFRQ 0 IEQFRQ 0 INBFRQ 10 IHBFRQ 0 -
    IUNREA -1 IUNWRI 31 IUNCRD 32 IUNVEL 33 KUNIT -1 -
    NSAVC 10 NSAVV 10 NPRINT 10 ISEED 314159 -
